POLICE are investigating after a man died on a tram in Edinburgh .
The death of the 74-year-old is being treated as &quot;unexplained&quot;.
Detectives were called to the Haymarket tram stop following reports that a man had become unwell.
Emergency services later pronounced the man dead at the scene.
